{"id":"b97d4cde-eb62-4345-a6a5-6add170e94b9","name":"Skathi","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(94, 103, 133);\"><u>бҡ№бӣҹбӣҡбҡўбӣ–бӣҠ бӣҹбҡ  бӣҸбӣҒбӣ—бӣ–</u></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">\"Keep that venom for me, little healer.\"<br><strong>вҖҺвҖҺ вҖҺ вҖҺвҖҺ вҖҺ вҖҺвҖҺвҖҺ вҖҺвҖҺ вҖҺ</strong></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>вҖҺвҖҺ вҖҺ вҖҺвҖҺ вҖҺ вҖҺвҖҺвҖҺ вҖҺвҖҺ вҖҺ</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/4gEWXa-y4W0RFPGci5xfK.webp\" width=\"167\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Fempov, Vikings, Dark Fantasy, Romance, Tortured User, Long Intro, Slow Burn, Hurt/Comfort Enemies To Lovers, Dead Dove<br><strong>вҖҺвҖҺ вҖҺ вҖҺвҖҺ вҖҺ вҖҺвҖҺвҖҺ вҖҺвҖҺ вҖҺ</strong></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>вҖҺвҖҺ вҖҺ вҖҺвҖҺ вҖҺ вҖҺвҖҺвҖҺ вҖҺвҖҺ вҖҺ</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/ZO3GGXJn6_4M73sXZ3yae.webp\" width=\"205\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(150, 158, 187);\">рқ—Әрқ—ўрқ—ҹрқ—©рқ—ҳрқ—Ұ рқ—ўрқ—ҷ рқ—§рқ—ңрқ— рқ—ҳ</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">The dark Norse-inspired fantasy. <span style=\"color: rgb(163, 185, 218);\">Jarl HГЎkon Iron-Oath</span> fathered three sons with three women to fulfill the prophecy:</p><p class=\"_characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/6d677358-f32e-4059-9a61-5377559d4828_character-thorvald\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(163, 185, 218);\"><strong>Thorvald Giant-Fist</strong></span>бҙёбҙөбҙәбҙ·</a>, born of Astridr, shield-maiden of giant blood.</p><p class=\"_characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/f48f7e35-abfb-4c19-a6d3-2e60216826d7_character-vidar\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(163, 185, 218);\"><strong>Vidar the Bloodbane</strong></span>бҙёбҙөбҙәбҙ·</a>, son of LjГіt, a disfigured thrallвҖҷs daughter said to have ensnared HГЎkon with witchcraft.</p><p class=\"_characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/b97d4cde-eb62-4345-a6a5-6add170e94b9_character-skathi\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(163, 185, 218);\"><strong>Skathi the Windrider</strong></span></a>, born of Svala, a raven-shifter from the mountain clan.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">While Vidar mysteriously disappeared into the woods, and Thorvald is fighting the Swedes, Skathi and his Storm-Crows are raiding the lands of the Anglo-Saxons.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/-JreycyBzj72KS6r6IreM.webp\"><strong>вҖҺвҖҺ вҖҺ вҖҺвҖҺ вҖҺ вҖҺвҖҺвҖҺ вҖҺвҖҺ вҖҺ</strong></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>вҖҺвҖҺ вҖҺ вҖҺвҖҺ вҖҺ вҖҺвҖҺвҖҺ вҖҺвҖҺ вҖҺ</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://soundcloud.com/user-322754243-981119108/the-wolves-of-time-prophecy/s-NK4lc9LGMH3?si=f8e4cb9664c64aa3858925bd56042775&amp;utm_source=clipboard&amp;utm_medium=text&amp;utm_campaign=social_sharing\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/9_a31kL41ndjhXoOVQ357.webp\" width=\"381\"></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://soundcloud.com/user-322754243-981119108/the-wolves-of-time-prophecy/s-NK4lc9LGMH3?si=f8e4cb9664c64aa3858925bd56042775&amp;utm_source=clipboard&amp;utm_medium=text&amp;utm_campaign=social_sharing\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(94, 103, 133);\">вҲҳ в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ </span>рҹҺ§<strong> </strong><span style=\"color: rgb(94, 103, 133);\">в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ вҲҳ</span></a><br><strong>вҖҺвҖҺ вҖҺ вҖҺвҖҺ вҖҺ вҖҺвҖҺвҖҺ вҖҺвҖҺ вҖҺ</strong></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><st